item.description:
@calebhammerlive did a whole video “responding” to me pointing out he is pushing a right wing narrative, and goes so far as to flagrantly lie about what’s said in a publically available video by me to defend himself. To his over 3 million followers. If you are gonna punch down like that at least make it land buddy. - so I’ll say it again, his editorial choices push a particular narrative, and he is way to politically incompetent to even defend from that allegation.<br>
